[
    {
        "text": "The ancient city of Florence changes slowly.",
        "startTime": 2494,
        "endTime": 5500,
        "slowStartTime": 3891,
        "slowEndTime": 8475
    },
    {
        "text": "Its narrow stone streets are much the same...",
        "startTime": 6561,
        "endTime": 8769,
        "slowStartTime": 9991,
        "slowEndTime": 13378
    },
    {
        "text": "...as when the Medici family ruled more than 500 years ago.",
        "startTime": 8857,
        "endTime": 11913,
        "slowStartTime": 13435,
        "slowEndTime": 18095
    },
    {
        "text": "The city has seen the Renaissance, the Industrial Revolution and the World Wars.",
        "startTime": 13553,
        "endTime": 17959,
        "slowStartTime": 20479,
        "slowEndTime": 27163
    },
    {
        "text": "All have affected it, but in one factory here, the ways of the past remain the same.",
        "startTime": 19052,
        "endTime": 24147,
        "slowStartTime": 28728,
        "slowEndTime": 36446
    },
    {
        "text": "The Antico Setificio Fiorentino, the antique silk factory of Florence.",
        "startTime": 24721,
        "endTime": 29903,
        "slowStartTime": 37232,
        "slowEndTime": 45080
    },
    {
        "text": "Here, the continuous noise of the old mechanical looms brings one back to the past.",
        "startTime": 35645,
        "endTime": 40544,
        "slowStartTime": 53618,
        "slowEndTime": 61041
    },
    {
        "text": "This noisy 19th century looms create some of the world's finest silk fabrics...",
        "startTime": 41093,
        "endTime": 45747,
        "slowStartTime": 61790,
        "slowEndTime": 68845
    },
    {
        "text": "...for draperies and upholstery.",
        "startTime": 45855,
        "endTime": 47269,
        "slowStartTime": 68933,
        "slowEndTime": 71128
    },
    {
        "text": "But here, they are the new machines.",
        "startTime": 47992,
        "endTime": 50169,
        "slowStartTime": 72138,
        "slowEndTime": 75478
    },
    {
        "text": "In another part of the factory, one can find the real pieces of history:...",
        "startTime": 51413,
        "endTime": 55178,
        "slowStartTime": 77270,
        "slowEndTime": 82992
    },
    {
        "text": "...looms that have been around for centuries.",
        "startTime": 55423,
        "endTime": 57419,
        "slowStartTime": 83285,
        "slowEndTime": 86354
    },
    {
        "text": "Stefano Benelli is a weaver who makes the silk fabric that machines alone cannot create.",
        "startTime": 58587,
        "endTime": 64364,
        "slowStartTime": 88031,
        "slowEndTime": 96771
    },
    {
        "text": "He stands over a huge loom and work slowly and carefully, weaving one thread at a time.",
        "startTime": 64653,
        "endTime": 70250,
        "slowStartTime": 97130,
        "slowEndTime": 105600
    },
    {
        "text": "Above him, there are special paper cards that carry the designs for complicated patterns.",
        "startTime": 73149,
        "endTime": 78101,
        "slowStartTime": 109873,
        "slowEndTime": 117376
    },
    {
        "text": "These looms were built in 1780, and they apply the same principles of weaving...",
        "startTime": 78933,
        "endTime": 83664,
        "slowStartTime": 118549,
        "slowEndTime": 125721
    },
    {
        "text": "...that were used for hundreds of years before that.",
        "startTime": 83783,
        "endTime": 86081,
        "slowStartTime": 125825,
        "slowEndTime": 129346
    },
    {
        "text": "Everything is done like it was done in the ancient time.",
        "startTime": 86525,
        "endTime": 90216,
        "slowStartTime": 129937,
        "slowEndTime": 135549
    },
    {
        "text": "But we continue to do an evolution, continuously, we invent.",
        "startTime": 90529,
        "endTime": 95799,
        "slowStartTime": 135943,
        "slowEndTime": 143924
    },
    {
        "text": "We create continuously but using the old looms.",
        "startTime": 95911,
        "endTime": 98570,
        "slowStartTime": 144016,
        "slowEndTime": 148080
    },
    {
        "text": "After the Second World War, other Italian silk manufacturers...",
        "startTime": 99839,
        "endTime": 103518,
        "slowStartTime": 149909,
        "slowEndTime": 155502
    },
    {
        "text": "...threw away their slower hand looms...",
        "startTime": 103619,
        "endTime": 105563,
        "slowStartTime": 155579,
        "slowEndTime": 158570
    },
    {
        "text": "...that left the Setificio alone in the handmade silk industry.",
        "startTime": 105895,
        "endTime": 109267,
        "slowStartTime": 158992,
        "slowEndTime": 164125
    },
    {
        "text": "There is a big difference between industrially produced silk and handwoven silk.",
        "startTime": 110009,
        "endTime": 114328,
        "slowStartTime": 165164,
        "slowEndTime": 171717
    },
    {
        "text": "Industrially produced silk usually has 3,000 to 4,000 threads running...",
        "startTime": 114715,
        "endTime": 118747,
        "slowStartTime": 172223,
        "slowEndTime": 178345
    },
    {
        "text": "...in one direction on a full piece of fabric.",
        "startTime": 118812,
        "endTime": 121103,
        "slowStartTime": 178368,
        "slowEndTime": 181879
    },
    {
        "text": "The silk produced on the old hand looms has 12,000 threads in the same amount of space.",
        "startTime": 121638,
        "endTime": 126647,
        "slowStartTime": 182607,
        "slowEndTime": 190196
    },
    {
        "text": "That's up to four times the number of threads that are used.",
        "startTime": 126932,
        "endTime": 129599,
        "slowStartTime": 190548,
        "slowEndTime": 194624
    },
    {
        "text": "This affects the quality of the silk including how it looks, sounds and feels.",
        "startTime": 130067,
        "endTime": 134488,
        "slowStartTime": 195251,
        "slowEndTime": 201957
    },
    {
        "text": "Factory director Sabine Pretsch points out that the color of the fabric...",
        "startTime": 136025,
        "endTime": 139621,
        "slowStartTime": 204188,
        "slowEndTime": 209657
    },
    {
        "text": "...is affected by the weaving process.",
        "startTime": 139699,
        "endTime": 141459,
        "slowStartTime": 209699,
        "slowEndTime": 212413
    },
    {
        "text": "Handwoven threads don't twist, so they show the full range of color in the silk.",
        "startTime": 141861,
        "endTime": 146017,
        "slowStartTime": 212941,
        "slowEndTime": 219251
    },
    {
        "text": "Hand weaving also brings out a slight red color in a beautiful softened effect in the fabric.",
        "startTime": 146396,
        "endTime": 151369,
        "slowStartTime": 219744,
        "slowEndTime": 227278
    },
    {
        "text": "Handmade silk also makes a special noise and better holds its shape.",
        "startTime": 151679,
        "endTime": 155318,
        "slowStartTime": 227668,
        "slowEndTime": 233202
    },
    {
        "text": "Even before the weaving begins,...",
        "startTime": 158095,
        "endTime": 160056,
        "slowStartTime": 237292,
        "slowEndTime": 240309
    },
    {
        "text": "...the silk threads are processed on machines that are 150 years old.",
        "startTime": 160241,
        "endTime": 163983,
        "slowStartTime": 240511,
        "slowEndTime": 246199
    },
    {
        "text": "Then, the threads are prepared according to how they will be used.",
        "startTime": 165458,
        "endTime": 168513,
        "slowStartTime": 248337,
        "slowEndTime": 252994
    },
    {
        "text": "The threads used for the wide part of the fabric are called the weft.",
        "startTime": 171035,
        "endTime": 174468,
        "slowStartTime": 256702,
        "slowEndTime": 261927
    },
    {
        "text": "These are carefully placed on a bobbin so that the threads are not twisted.",
        "startTime": 176799,
        "endTime": 180855,
        "slowStartTime": 265348,
        "slowEndTime": 271507
    },
    {
        "text": "The threads used for the warp, or the long part of the fabric,...",
        "startTime": 183036,
        "endTime": 186302,
        "slowStartTime": 274704,
        "slowEndTime": 279678
    },
    {
        "text": "...are gathered together to create long groups.",
        "startTime": 186485,
        "endTime": 188826,
        "slowStartTime": 279877,
        "slowEndTime": 283464
    },
    {
        "text": "But again, not twisted.",
        "startTime": 189389,
        "endTime": 190930,
        "slowStartTime": 284233,
        "slowEndTime": 286620
    },
    {
        "text": "The fabrics made at the Setificio can't be found in stores or anywhere else.",
        "startTime": 194295,
        "endTime": 198816,
        "slowStartTime": 291593,
        "slowEndTime": 298449
    },
    {
        "text": "Every piece of cloth is custom made.",
        "startTime": 199219,
        "endTime": 201445,
        "slowStartTime": 298979,
        "slowEndTime": 302392
    },
    {
        "text": "But what may seem like difficult and boring work to some people...",
        "startTime": 201892,
        "endTime": 205259,
        "slowStartTime": 302988,
        "slowEndTime": 308113
    },
    {
        "text": "...is enjoyable to a craftsman like Benelli.",
        "startTime": 205407,
        "endTime": 207831,
        "slowStartTime": 308261,
        "slowEndTime": 311972
    },
    {
        "text": "In the mind, it's okay. Not stressful.",
        "startTime": 208447,
        "endTime": 214292,
        "slowStartTime": 312821,
        "slowEndTime": 321663
    },
    {
        "text": "It's been said that no other city has maintained...",
        "startTime": 215509,
        "endTime": 218181,
        "slowStartTime": 323414,
        "slowEndTime": 327497
    },
    {
        "text": "...the art and beauty of the Renaissance like Florence.",
        "startTime": 218302,
        "endTime": 221152,
        "slowStartTime": 327603,
        "slowEndTime": 331953
    },
    {
        "text": "It may be appropriate then, that here at the city's Antico Setificio Fiorentino,...",
        "startTime": 221403,
        "endTime": 226186,
        "slowStartTime": 332255,
        "slowEndTime": 339504
    },
    {
        "text": "...style and tradition come together in beautiful handwoven silk fabrics.",
        "startTime": 226320,
        "endTime": 230935,
        "slowStartTime": 339630,
        "slowEndTime": 346627
    },
    {
        "text": "It seems that the Setificio has perfected the art of making silk.",
        "startTime": 231202,
        "endTime": 235631,
        "slowStartTime": 346953,
        "slowEndTime": 353672
    }
]